SUMMARY:Unionize for Trans Rights - Campaign Kickoff
DTSTAMP:20260403T051350Z
DTSTART:20260403T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Interested in exploring what a labor-focused approach to winnin
	g trans rights might look like? Come help brainstorm and sketch out the ea
	rly phases of our Unionize for Trans Rights​ campaign! \\nWe’ll be at Big 
	Time Brewery​ in the U District for a working-social where we’ll discuss h
	ow we can help trans and nonbinary workers organize their workplaces and e
	nshrine protections into union contracts. This is also an opportunity for 
	those looking to get involved with this campaign to get to know one anothe
	r—we hope you’ll join us! \\nRSVP here!\n\nhttps://seattledsa.org/event/un
