DESCRIPTION:War in Iran\\nWhere is this heading and how do we fight it?\\nT
	his Sunday\\\, April 5\\n5pm\\nVictrola Cafe (411 15th Ave E) Community ro
	om\\n  \\nThe war rages unabated.  Where is this heading? Will there be a 
	ground invasion? Nuclear weapons? What does the war tell us about US and I
	sraeli imperialism? How can the socialist movement\\\, the labor movement\
	\\, and the Left build a fighting anti-war movement? \\nWe’ll also discuss
